data.description: OPEN HOUSE 11/19/23 Sun, 12:30 - 2:30. You will love this move-in ready multi with so much space to stretch out. Updated through the years with roof 2018, HVAC Nov. ''23, an updated kitchen & newer appliances, some exterior siding replaced & exterior paint, water heater 2021, newer carpet in living room, some interior new paint. The conforming lower level 4th bedroom is great for an older child.  Kitchen has a pantry. It has a big flat fenced backyard with a newer 16 x 16  shed for all your yard items and a big deck for entertaining.  Close proximity to I-80 with easy access to downtown or even Lincoln, Bellevue, and Papillion.  The kitchen refrigerator is included.
